    "heroSub": "A photographer and storyteller chasing the few seconds where <strong>light, a stranger, and a wall agree</strong> to make a photograph — shot and shared as <strong>Kahaani Baaz</strong>.",
    "aboutParagraphs": [
      "Mateen shoots under the name <strong>Kahaani Baaz</strong> — Urdu for \"the one who tells stories.\" It started as a way to notice things: a chalk portrait sketched onto a sunlit wall, a kitten watching from an alley, a city waking up in gold light before the noise starts.",
      "The eye is documentary first — <strong>unposed, patient, curious about ordinary moments</strong> — and it moves between still frames and short-form video, looking for the same thing either way: a few honest seconds worth holding onto.",
      "Every frame gets shared back to the same place it came from — the street, the people on it, and whoever's scrolling past at the right moment."
    ]
  },
